data.description: Welcome home!  Nestled within the serene gated community of Blanco Bluffs, this charming two-story residence exudes an air of elegance and comfort. Boasting a contemporary design, the home offers a perfect fusion of functionality and style, catering to both relaxation and entertainment needs. Upon entering the main level features a large living room with a cozy wood burning fire place, sleek kitchen with a central island, and two dining areas. Upstairs, three cozy bedrooms, including a large luxurious primary suite with a spa-like bathroom complete with a double vanity and walk-in closet. Outside, the property offers plenty of space for outdoor entertaining and relaxation! Take a tour today of your new home.
